org.melior.client.core

Class ClientObject<C extends ClientConfig,T extends ExceptionTarget,P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.melior.client.core.ClientObject<C,T,P>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InvocationHandler, ExceptionTarget

    public abstract class ClientObject<C extends ClientConfig,T extends ExceptionTarget,P>
extends Object
implements ExceptionTarget, InvocationHandler
    Base class for managed objects that form part of a remoting client, but that are not connection objects. A client object may be cached by its parent. A client object may have a connection object as its parent.
    Since:
    2.3
    Author:
    Melior
